headline: FactSet (FDS) Stock Trades Down, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of financial data provider FactSet (NYSE:FDS) fell 3.1% in the afternoon session after markets continued to decline, as investors grew cautious ahead of a key speech by Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell.
